Itu Hyogo

97
00:13:15.140 --> 00:13:18.040
Dia pekerja keras

98
00:13:18.210 --> 00:13:20.310
Alita Ayo pergi

99
00:13:26.430 --> 00:13:27.800
Hyugo...

100
00:13:27.850 --> 00:13:28.870
Ayo pergi

101
00:14:45.250 --> 00:14:47.490
Pengemudi yang ketakutan itu
